alue problem. We emphasize the local\naspect of this result by applying it to an example for which the identification\nof the equilibria in the cell boundary of $\\mathcal{O}$ is obtained from the\nknowledge of only a section of the Sturm meander $\\mathcal{M}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Feb 2020 14:27:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Apr 2021 15:07:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-12"}
